**Bi-directional One-To-One association
** In a bidirectional relationship, we can fetch the details of two related entities by querying each entity separately. In other words, we can navigate from one entity to another entity and vise-versa
**Book and Publisher. A renowned author gave his/her Book to a Publisher to publish or in other words, the Publisher used to publish a Book of a renowned author. 
**Take a look at the definition of Publisher and Book

// Publisher class
  public class Publisher {
      private int id = 0;
      …
      private Book book;
      …
  }
// Book class
  public class Book {
      private int id = 0;
      …
      private Publisher publisher;
      …
  }